OL,3,C'Frenzied' knife attack suspect
OL,4,Cdetained by workers, court told
OL,6,FWorkers at an office building detained
OL,7,Fa man as he carried out a "frenzied"
OL,8,Fknife attack in a bid to kill his ex-
OL,9,Fpartner at her place of work, a court
OL,10,Fhas heard.
OL,12,FAnwar Ashraf, 38, is on trial at
OL,13,FWinchester Crown Court charged with
OL,14,Fthe attempted murder of Carla Skeites
OL,15,Fat the premises 3600 Parkway in
OL,16,FWhiteley, Hampshire, at about 9am on
OL,17,FApril 30 2025.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
