PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1774278664
OL,3,C'Frenzied' knife attack suspect
OL,4,Cdetained by workers, court told
OL,6,FGiles Bedloe, prosecuting, told the
OL,7,Fjury that the defendant had pleaded
OL,8,Fguilty to wounding with intent to
OL,9,Fcause grievous bodily harm and
OL,10,Fpossession of a knife, but he denied
OL,11,Fthat he wanted to kill her.
OL,13,FThe prosecutor said: "He was caught
OL,14,Fred-handed, he was restrained in the
OL,15,Flobby of the office building and then
OL,16,Fwas detained by other members of the
OL,17,Fpublic."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
