OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1774278664
OL,3,C'Frenzied' knife attack suspect
OL,4,Cdetained by workers, court told
OL,6,FMr Bedloe said that the defendant and
OL,7,FMs Skeites had not been in a
OL,8,Frelationship for several weeks but he
OL,9,Fadded that Ashraf had become
OL,10,F"obsessed" with her and accused her of
OL,11,F"cheating" on him.
OL,13,FHe said: "Mr Ashraf was obsessed with
OL,14,FMs Skeites, he had been ringing her
OL,15,Foff the hook and bombarding her with
OL,16,Fmessages."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
