OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1774278664
OL,3,C'Frenzied' knife attack suspect
OL,4,Cdetained by workers, court told
OL,6,FThe prosecutor stated that the
OL,7,Fdefendant was restrained by members of
OL,8,Fthe public with one man kicking his
OL,9,Flegs to knock him over before blocking
OL,10,Fhis exit.
OL,12,FHe said that this man described seeing
OL,13,F"blood spurting out of her", while the
OL,14,Fdefendant had blood on his hands.
OL,16,FMr Bedloe also said that a colleague
OL,17,Fscreamed when she saw Ms Skeites, and
OL,18,Fsaid: "She was hysterical seeing her
OL,19,Fboss in that state."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1774278664
OL,3,C'Frenzied' knife attack suspect
OL,4,Cdetained by workers, court told
OL,6,FAnother worker attempted to administer
OL,7,Ffirst aid and described the "terrified
OL,8,Flook" on Ms Skeites' face
OL,10,FMr Bedloe added: "Carla Skeites was
OL,11,Frushed to hospital as she sustained
OL,12,Fmultiple injuries as a result of this
OL,13,Ffrenzied attack including 17
OL,14,Findividual stab wounds."
OL,16,FHe said that as Ashraf was detained by
OL,17,Fpolice he said: "What would you do if
OL,18,Fyour partner cheated on you, how would
OL,19,Fyou react?"
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
