PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1774278664
OL,3,C'Frenzied' knife attack suspect
OL,4,Cdetained by workers, court told
OL,6,FMr Bedloe said: "He admitted what he
OL,7,Fhad done, he said he only wanted to
OL,8,Fscare her, he didn't want to kill her."
OL,10,FAshraf, previously of Southsea, denies
OL,11,Fthe charge and the trial continues.
